{"tid":1410172,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"油塘有無人一齊塞","createTime":"2019-08-05T00:51:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T01:58:53.000Z","uid":232181,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1228301818459c0b52fb04a25ece21b0d52dd83f","tid":1410172,"uid":232181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:51:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>好多東九龍返港島東的朋友都想被罷工</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b02cdf4b481b50ce4777dbfb9fb4b8caa64d8349","tid":1410172,"uid":232181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:51:44.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b23c0732f2ba75bee8fa3a5f6c4d6f88b520eac9","tid":1410172,"uid":232181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:52:05.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"b2b1e470e50b74c88385ad4afdce1b1121fca896","tid":1410172,"uid":280199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:52:38.000Z","msg":"4號月台 塞死 4-1車門"},{"pid":"7a2a79ff8a94b0d6780c08410b4918e953b7b9d2","tid":1410172,"uid":99001,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:53:01.000Z","msg":"如果俾人插可以咁對答<br />\n➡️阻住我返工<br />\n❌粗口<br />\n⭕️我都好想返工啊<br />\n➡️阻住我哋啲市民/冇人支持你㗎<br />\n❌阻乜x嘢啊<br />\n⭕️支持警察執法（成立獨立調查委員會）<br />\n➡️你咪去攪林鄭囉，攪我地啲小市民做嘜？<br />\n⭕️係林鄭搞緊小市民<br />\n⭕️係囉，佢唔出黎喎，要求政府回應！佢月薪40萬咖<br />\n⭕️唔好搞人屋企咁冇品，人地都有屋企人，屋企人係無辜咖！<br />\n⭕️林鄭好多屋企，唔知佢訓邊<br />\n⭕️林鄭成個政府都冇鬼用，淨係識搵警察出黎打人，自己就匿埋，搞到愈來愈多人出黎示威<br />\n(將責任推俾政府，強調示威者都係被逼)<br />\n➡️本人撐你都變到唔撐啦<br />\n⭕️請你體諒，宜家每星期都有好多流血衝突，好多年輕人受重傷，咁落去香港就黎打仗乜都冇，堵錢堵路已經係最和平嘅方法去施壓俾政府<br />\n⭕️其實我哋而家唔係要爭取同意,係希望政府可以回應依家社會發生緊嘅嘢<br />\n⭕️你唔需要撐我，撐警察就得，支持成立獨立調査委員會😂<br />\n➡️成班死癈青，淨係識攪事<br />\n⭕️今日好多律師會計師公務員都罷工呀，政府太過分，天怒人怨<br />\n⭕️如果政府真係有做嘢就唔會咁多死癈青啦，收納税人咁多錢又唔做嘢，一日到黑只係識得譴責！<br />\n➡️粗口<br />\n❌粗口回應<br />\n⭕️嘩支持政府嘅人咁暴力嘅😱<br />\n⭕️嘩！問候我哋呢啲小市民<br />\n⭕️你與其責備我地搞事不如責備下呢個暴力制度嘅政府<br />\n⭕️我明嘅，你係想鬧個政府搞到啲人出黎示威<br />\n⭕️我都好嬲呀，講左咁多次訴求，政府都漠示民意<br />\n⭕️車長！有人講粗口，違反香港鐵路附例呀！罰佢$5000！"},{"pid":"22ed0a52d61c3db755d61f51d43040c69dbc51b4","tid":1410172,"uid":232181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T00:54:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0e37920d382787ba40f5775ef5837a6be4a12e19","tid":1410172,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:30:20.000Z","msg":"到咗"},{"pid":"01e2f62ac6ca3ad9f9188ba3245567c3fd682aaa","tid":1410172,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eCZXGTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeCZXGTu.jpg&h=fedeb5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油塘發生緊口角"},{"pid":"c3a28adf85b929493d7926bd4abdd32df5518758","tid":1410172,"uid":5627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e2f62ac6ca3ad9f9188ba3245567c3fd682aaa","tid":1410172,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eCZXGTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeCZXGTu.jpg&h=fedeb5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油塘發生緊口角"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:34:12.000Z","msg":"油塘仲未封站咩"},{"pid":"859172ed0f8fce122bddba1c2d34b6c587e34e5d","tid":1410172,"uid":270281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e2f62ac6ca3ad9f9188ba3245567c3fd682aaa","tid":1410172,"uid":245670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:32:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eCZXGTu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeCZXGTu.jpg&h=fedeb5a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油塘發生緊口角"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:34:15.000Z","msg":"啲人係咪咁想返工呀"},{"pid":"ccdea929fee565b6d7a0e14e91cea3f961a23718","tid":1410172,"uid":4204,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T01:39:50.000Z","msg":"係咪流料嚟？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6hux2Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6hux2Q.png&h=5a3f5557&s={SIZE}\" />